                <section id="servicii-detalii">
                    <h3>Detalii si calcul pret</h3>
                    <h4>Calculul Pretului Final cu Reducere</h4>
                    <p>Formula pentru calcularea pretului final dupa aplicarea unei reduceri procentuale:</p>
                    <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                        <mrow>
                            <msub>
                                <mi>P</mi>
                                <mi>final</mi>
                            </msub>
                            <mo>=</mo>
                            <msub>
                                <mi>P</mi>
                                <mi>original</mi>
                            </msub>
                            <mo>x</mo>
                            <mfenced>
                                <mrow>
                                    <mn>1</mn>
                                    <mo>-</mo>
                                    <mfrac>
                                        <mi>R</mi>
                                        <mn>100</mn>
                                    </mfrac>
                                </mrow>
                            </mfenced>
                        </mrow>
                    </math>
                    <p><small>unde P_original = pretul initial, R = reducere in procente, P_final = pretul dupa reducere</small></p>

